title: "Cross-Lingual LLM Safety Evaluation"
authors:
  - family-names: "Neelapareddigari"
    given-names: "Praneetha"
date-released: 2026-07-07
url: "https://github.com/praneethaneelapareddigari/cross-lingual-llm-safety-eval"
license: MIT
version: "0.1.0-pilot"
repository-code: "https://github.com/praneethaneelapareddigari/cross-lingual-llm-safety-eval"
abstract: >
  A multilingual benchmark evaluating whether LLM safety behavior — refusal,
  harmfulness, over-refusal — holds consistently across languages and
  regions, using a paired-statistics framework (McNemar, Wilson CI,
  bootstrap CI, Cohen's h, Cohen's Kappa). Status: pilot in progress.
